msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc83:0.3"
msgid "Pācittiyakaṇḍa"
msgstr "The chapter on confession"
#. VAR: Ratanavagga → rājavagga (^pi-tv-pvr1.1#209 [Kattha­paññat­ti­vāra/5. Rājavagga] ^pi-tv-pvr1.2#143 [Katāpattivāra/5. Rājavagga])
